			<description><![CDATA[<h2 style="color: rgb(60, 148, 48);">
Who We Are</h2>
<p>
We are a national strategic business plan consulting and investment banking firm.</p>
<p>
We specialize in assisting emerging and middle market companies with equity and debt financings and with selling all or part of their businesses.</p>
<p>
We conduct market research, prepare business plans, and represent and promote our client companies to financial and strategic investors and acquirers.</p>
<p>
Please learn more about us at www.growthink.com.</p>
<p>
As we are currently in a high growth mode, we are looking for the right individuals to contribute to and participate in our Company expansion.&nbsp;</p>
<h2 style="color: rgb(60, 148, 48);">
The Position</h2>
<p>
As a Growthink Director of Investor Relations working from our Los Angeles headquarters, you will &nbsp;work with Company principals to manage company financing &nbsp;assignments.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p>
Our client assignments primarily involve circulating investment offerings, via the telephone and email correspondence, to prospective investors - banks, private equity firms, venture capitalists, and individual investors.</p>
<h2 style="color: rgb(60, 148, 48);">
Qualifications</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<u>Burning desire to succeed, extremely client-oriented, highly motivated, and NEVER say die</u></li>
<li>
Significant investment banking and /or financial sales (brokerage) experience</li>
<li>
A deep and abiding passion for entrepreneurship and its place in effecting meaningful change for the better in the world</li>
<li>
Ability to engage entrepreneurs, business owners and investors in meaningful, creative, high trust conversations to assess their needs and objectives</li>
<li>
Proven ability to raise capital</li>
<li>
Proximity to our LAX office (Century Blvd.) location</li>
<li>
Active FINRA Series 79 Licensing a significant plus</li>
</ul>
<h2 style="margin-top: 10px; color: rgb(60, 148, 48);">
Compensation</h2>
<ul>
<li>
Salary plus Commission plus Bonus</li>
<li>
Health and Hospital Benefits</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
